metadata.name: Immersion
metadata.description:
In the picture, a girl in a bright hat, she may seem like a foreign object, too bright against the background of greenery.
But she is reborn, crouched like an embryo in the womb, one eye closed, almost ready to merge with the outside world.  
Maybe she is sleeping, maybe she is immersed in a meditative slumber, or maybe she will indeed soon sprout flowers and become a plant herself...
